              "free_text": [
                " D(d,n) source"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In the course of a run, the neutron flux was",
                "continuously monitored by means of a calibrated long",
                "counter set at 90.degr. with respect to the deuteron",
                "beam. The charge collected at the target cell was",
                "integrated simultaneously and all the data runs made",
                "for a constant integrated charge."
              ]
            }
          ],
